50|$|In 2010, 2.5 tonnes of waste, {{including}} 13 kg of 80% enriched uranium, {{were transported}} from Vinča to a reprocessing facility at Mayak, Russia. This was <b>the</b> <b>IAEA's</b> largest ever technical cooperation project, {{and thousands of}} police protected the convoys.|$|R
